stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Disconnected
    
    Disconnected --> Connecting : User Input 57600 baud
    
    Connecting --> Port_Open : navigator.serial.requestPort success
    Connecting --> Error : Access Denied or Port Busy
    
    Port_Open --> Reading : Start infinite reader.read loop
    
    Reading --> Parsing : Uint8Array chunk received
    Parsing --> Reading : Magic Byte 0xFD processed
    
    Reading --> Buffer_Overrun : Chromium buffer saturation
    Buffer_Overrun --> Cleanup : Catch overrun exception
    
    Reading --> Disconnected : User requests disconnect
    
    Cleanup --> Reconnecting : Exponential Backoff Wait 150ms
    Reconnecting --> Port_Open : Retry port.open
    Reconnecting --> Error : Max retries exceeded
    
    Error --> Disconnected : Reset state variables
